window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>All alone in a dangerous galaxy — a new civilization struggles for survival. War rages across the galaxy. Difficult diplomacy is all that keeps Carter Ash and his people safe from the threats around them.<br> <br> They need all the time they can get to build their home, because every day new, hungry eyes turn towards their fledgling government and their resource rich moon.<br> <br> Even now, multiple invading fleets race towards Carter’s home — and it’ll take everything he’s got to be ready for the fight of his life.<br> <br> And to top it off, a blast from his past arrives, complicating everything.<br> <br> The War Game: Homecoming is a LitRPG novel for discerning adults.</p>"; 
